Regular Cakes

There are many kinds of cakes found in the market. Some of the popular and in-demand online cakes delivery varieties are regular cakes, eggless cakes, 5 star cakes, fruit cakes, designer cakes, cup cakes, chocolate cakes, pineapple cakes, lemon cakes, carrot cakes, black forest cakes, butterscotch cakes, strawberry cakes, and vanilla cakes to name to a few. To send flowers and regular cakes online in India, you can try out our exhaustive assortment of cakes. If you choose to purchase or gift our luscious lemon vanilla cakes, you wouldn't be disappointed. These cakes are filled with the goodness of vanilla essence and lemon juice and some wonderful cherry reds are placed on top of the cake to give a designer look. You can gift this tasty treat to your loved ones along with choicest flowers, chocolates or fruits hamper.

Variety of Regular Cake

Some of our regular cakes include:
o Multi-coloured Rainbow vanilla cakes
o Customised photo printed cakes

o Mouth watering dark chocolate cakes
o Lovingly designed fruit cakes
o Simple happy birthday cakes
You can choose the category of service. For instance, you can order same day cake delivery in India or a special midnight delivery facility as per your immediate requirement. Prices may vary according to the service that is chosen. We promise you to provide cakes are made from A-grade quality ingredients and produced by experienced master bakers. Call us at the earliest to send regular cakes in India within a short timeframe. We guarantee you the finest and superior cake varieties that taste heavenly and made available to our valued customers at reasonable price rates.
